      <hr /><a name="skip_menu"></a><h1><span>008</span> - <span>Books</span><span> (NR)</span></h1>
      <hr />
      <div class="formatname">MARC 21 Bibliographic - full</div>
      <div class="datename">April 2015</div>
      <hr />
      <h4>Indicators and Subfield Codes</h4>
      <div class="wildcard">
         <div>
            <p>Field has no indicators or subfield codes; the data
               				elements are positionally defined.
            </p>
         </div>
      </div>
